article_id:924,category_name:News,title_name:New Very Hard Difficulty Added to the Main Campaign!,image_path:,message:<div>A new difficulty level, Very Hard, was added to the main campaign at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576476000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/cb35a2e2037d4b93418331854c4f92e1.png"></div><div><br></div><div>When you clear quests on Very Hard difficulty, you will get Dyrenell Aureus, various royal insignias, and items that confer augments as first clear rewards!<br><br>A new material item used to unlock mana nodes on the sixth mana circle, which will be implemented for certain characters after the next update, will also drop from these quests!<br><br>Note:<br>Very Hard difficulty will unlock for each chapter after a player has cleared Ch. 10 / 6-3 &quot;A New Vow,&quot; as well as Hard difficulty for that chapter.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<br><br></div>,start_time:1576476000,update_time1575538855